11:Tfc2,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What budget do I need to get started?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Most clients invest $2,500 to $15,000 per month in management plus ad spend. We tailor scope to your goals and provide clear pricing after a strategy call."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How quickly will I see results?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Paid media produces data within days and meaningful optimization within 2 to 4 weeks. ROAS typically improves significantly by month 2 or 3 as we refine targeting and creative."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you require long-term contracts?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. We work month to month because results should earn retention, not contract lock-in."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do you report performance?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Weekly optimization notes and monthly dashboards covering spend, ROAS, CPL, conversion rate, and revenue attribution where tracking allows."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you manage Performance Max campaigns?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We build and optimize PMax with proper asset groups, audience signals, and feed data. We also monitor search term insights to prevent PMax from cannibalizing branded Search traffic."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Will I own my Google Ads account?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Always. We work inside your account with full admin access. If you leave, you keep every campaign, keyword list, and conversion setup we built."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which ad platforms do you manage?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Google Ads, Meta, LinkedIn, and Microsoft Ads. We recommend the mix based on where your buyers actually convert, not platform hype."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you set up conversion tracking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. GA4, GTM, call tracking, and offline conversion import are standard in week one. We do not optimize blind."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you work with our in-house team?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We collaborate with internal marketers, other agencies, and fractional leaders. We can lead the program or fill a specific channel gap."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What industries do you serve?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Home services, healthcare, professional services, SaaS, e-commerce, and manufacturing. If your buyers search before they buy, we can usually help."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Cuánto cuesta la gestión Google Ads?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Las tarifas de gestión parten en $1,500 al mes para cuentas bajo $10,000 de ad spend. Cuentas más grandes se cotizan al 12% al 15% del gasto. Tu presupuesto de anuncios se paga directo a Google. Recomendamos mínimo $3,000 mensuales de ad spend para reunir datos suficientes de optimización."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Gestionan campañas Performance Max?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Sí. Construimos y optimizamos Performance Max con asset groups correctos, señales de audiencia y datos de feed para e-commerce. También monitoreamos search term insights y tráfico de brand para evitar que PMax canibalice tus campañas Search."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Qué tan rápido veré resultados de Google Ads?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Las campañas Search suelen generar leads en la primera semana de lanzamiento. CPL estable y optimizado normalmente toma 30 a 45 días mientras refinamos keywords, negativas y pujas. Shopping y PMax pueden necesitar 2 a 3 semanas para que el algoritmo se estabilice."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Seré dueño de mi cuenta Google Ads?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Siempre. Trabajamos dentro de tu cuenta con acceso admin completo. Si te vas, te quedas con cada campaña, lista de keywords y setup de conversiones que construimos."}}]}6:[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/#organization\",\"name\":\"KINEXIS Digital\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/assets/logos/KINEXIS_icon_logo.webp\",\"width\":512,\"height\":512},\"description\":\"Digital marketing agency specializing in SEO, paid media, web design, CRO, and analytics for local businesses, SaaS companies, and enterprise organizations.\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/kinexisdigital\"],\"contactPoint\":{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"sales\",\"email\":\"hello@kinexisdigital.com\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"English\",\"Spanish\"]}}"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/es/services/google-ads#service\",\"name\":\"Google Ads Management\",\"description\":\"Gestión Google Ads para Search, Shopping y Performance Max. Optimización de Quality Score, tracking de conversiones y campañas enfocadas en ROAS. Desde…\",\"provider\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/#organization\"},\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/es/services/google-ads\",\"areaServed\":{\"@type\":\"Country\",\"name\":\"Worldwide\"}}"}}],["$","script","2",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$11"}}],"$L12"],"$L13","$L14"]
